---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Teach Children Math
description: Free, open-source math app with 150 scripted lessons, 341 practice problems, and interactive flashcards. Built on Direct Instruction methodology for ages 5-10.
bodyClass: page-home
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__inner">
    <h1 class="hero__title">Teach Children Math</h1>
    <p class="hero__subtitle">150 scripted lessons. 341 practice problems. Interactive flashcards. Built on proven Direct Instruction methodology. Free, open source, no accounts required.</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a href="/lessons/" class="btn btn--cta">Start Lessons</a>
      <a href="/guide/" class="btn btn--outline">Teacher Guide</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Stats bar #}
<section class="home-stats">
  <div class="home-stats__inner">
    <div class="home-stat">
      <span class="home-stat__number">150</span>
      <span class="home-stat__label">Lessons</span>
    </div>
    <div class="home-stat">
      <span class="home-stat__number">2,400+</span>
      <span class="home-stat__label">Teaching Steps</span>
    </div>
    <div class="home-stat">
      <span class="home-stat__number">341</span>
      <span class="home-stat__label">Practice Problems</span>
    </div>
    <div class="home-stat">
      <span class="home-stat__number">7</span>
      <span class="home-stat__label">Phases</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <div class="home-section__inner">
    <h2 class="home-section__title">How It Works</h2>
    <div class="method-cards">
      <div class="method-card">
        <span class="method-card__number">1</span>
        <h3 class="method-card__title">Read the Script</h3>
        <p class="method-card__text">Each lesson tells you exactly what to say and do. No teaching experience needed. Just read and follow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="method-card">
        <span class="method-card__number">2</span>
        <h3 class="method-card__title">Child Follows Visuals</h3>
        <p class="method-card__text">Numbers, dot patterns, and number lines guide the learner through each concept with immediate feedback.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="method-card">
        <span class="method-card__number">3</span>
        <h3 class="method-card__title">Practice &amp; Review</h3>
        <p class="method-card__text">Each lesson is 90% review and 10% new material. Flashcards and practice sets reinforce every skill.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section home-section--alt">
  <div class="home-section__inner">
    <h2 class="home-section__title">7 Phases, From Counting to Arithmetic</h2>
    <p class="home-section__subtitle">Every phase builds on the last. Master one before moving to the next.</p>
    <div class="phase-cards">
      {% for phase in phases %}
      <a href="/phases/{{ phase.slug }}/" class="phase-card">
        <span class="phase-card__badge">Phase {{ phase.id }}</span>
        <h3 class="phase-card__title">{{ phase.title | replace("Phase " + phase.id + ": ", "") }}</h3>
        <p class="phase-card__desc">Lessons {{ phase.lessonRange }}. {{ phase.description | truncate(100) }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section">
  <div class="home-section__inner">
    <h2 class="home-section__title">Practice &amp; Flashcards</h2>
    <p class="home-section__subtitle">Reinforce what you learn with interactive problem sets and customizable flashcard decks.</p>
    <div class="method-cards">
      <div class="method-card">
        <span class="method-card__number" style="background:var(--green-50);color:var(--green-700)">25</span>
        <h3 class="method-card__title">Practice Sets</h3>
        <p class="method-card__text">Interactive problem sets for every phase. Instant feedback, scoring, and streak tracking.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="method-card">
        <span class="method-card__number" style="background:var(--amber-50);color:var(--amber-700)">341</span>
        <h3 class="method-card__title">Problems</h3>
        <p class="method-card__text">Counting, comparing, addition, subtraction, place value, regrouping, and word problems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="method-card">
        <span class="method-card__number" style="background:var(--rose-50);color:var(--rose-700)">&#x2764;</span>
        <h3 class="method-card__title">Flashcards</h3>
        <p class="method-card__text">Filter by phase, type, and difficulty. Wrong answers re-enter the deck for extra practice.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:var(--space-xl);display:flex;gap:var(--space-md);justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <a href="/practice/" class="btn btn--cta">Practice Sets</a>
      <a href="/flashcards/" class="btn btn--outline" style="color:var(--text-primary);border-color:var(--border-color)">Flashcards</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="home-section home-section--alt">
  <div class="home-section__inner" style="text-align:center">
    <h2 class="home-section__title">100% Free. No Accounts. No Tracking.</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);max-width:36rem;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">Math Direct is open source and works entirely in your browser. Progress is saved locally on your device. No sign-ups, no ads, no data collection.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:var(--space-md);justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <a href="/lessons/" class="btn btn--cta">Start Teaching</a>
      <a href="/features/" class="btn btn--outline" style="color:var(--text-primary);border-color:var(--border-color)">See All Features</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
